ATARI  UPDATE the new A5 size Atari mag has finished  after  only 
one issue. It's a shame for two reasons, the first is we could do 
with another mag - even if it was a ST HANDBOOK clone. The second 
is  that I spent money promoting it and I feel a bit  hacked  off 
about it. It's not just the money,I feel I may have lost a bit of 
credibility with the people who ordered it from me.

